{"tid":549802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[19出來講幾句]原來鄧永鏘係空心佬倌","createTime":"2018-02-04T04:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T20:42:00.000Z","uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"74d7d5b5c78da922e67ffbf0a51fd007dd5a10e7","tid":549802,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T04:57:21.000Z","msg":"原文自已入去睇，好長 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">He's the 'tycoon' who lived a life of lavish generosity. But six months after his death, Sir David Tang's society pals are asking... did the party king die a pauper?</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2018/02/03/23/48DB8BCE00000578-5348901-image-m-21_1517700613242.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2018%2F02%2F03%2F23%2F48DB8BCE00000578-5348901-image-m-21_1517700613242.jpg&h=ec396434&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Sir David Tang led a life of barely believable opulence, a crucible melding the worlds of fashion, royalty, business and art. He is pictured with model and actress Sienna Miller in 2011<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2018/02/03/23/48DB8BDC00000578-5348901-image-a-22_1517700684461.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2018%2F02%2F03%2F23%2F48DB8BDC00000578-5348901-image-a-22_1517700684461.jpg&h=a445cfb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n A growing number of people have told The Mail on Sunday they believe Tang (above, with supermodel Naomi Campbell in 2012) died almost penniless<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2018/02/03/23/48DB8C0A00000578-5348901-image-m-25_1517700732519.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2018%2F02%2F03%2F23%2F48DB8C0A00000578-5348901-image-m-25_1517700732519.jpg&h=b2b25b53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Among close friends, it was no secret that Tang was a committed gambler. Also a tireless donor-fundraiser, he was happy to bankroll causes close to his heart, including both charities and friends. It is said, for example, he had been particularly generous to Sarah, Duchess of York (above, with him in 2002)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2018/02/03/23/48DB8C1400000578-5348901-image-m-27_1517700755872.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2018%2F02%2F03%2F23%2F48DB8C1400000578-5348901-image-m-27_1517700755872.jpg&h=a72d5540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n In recent years, a &pound;1.5 million tax bill handed out by HMRC, in response to Tang overstaying his &lsquo;non-dom&rsquo; status in the UK by one day, suggested he was not fully in control of his finances. (Above, with Pippa Middleton in 2013)<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5348901/David-Tangs-society-pals-asking-died-pauper.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-5348901%2FDavid-Tangs-society-pals-asking-died-pauper.html&d=DnNAoCEY61nQzabBFrNAfEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=22a62131\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5348901/David-Tangs-society-pals-asking-died-pauper.html</a>"},{"pid":"5d1dadd47cbd549796284d0b2d7819305114011c","tid":549802,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:21:36.000Z","msg":"都好呀，起碼到死都未使捱窮，死後點空心都唔使理"},{"pid":"88995975b5797327511ca6ab240bba1ddc3cb6c9","tid":549802,"uid":12554,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:25:47.000Z","msg":"自己錢自己用晒<br />\n都唔算空心老倌掛<br />\n又唔係好似wrong hole咁開空頭支票"},{"pid":"4cb96f3b38eaca1f2cb5bb2e2d384615781664cf","tid":549802,"uid":6352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:28:53.000Z","msg":"佢阿爺留下唔少野，空心極有限。"},{"pid":"79c47ea058273fb8ca2b85ff2bae1e4d43ee8160","tid":549802,"uid":79563,"